OL,3,CMobuoy dump: #100m dump continues to
OL,4,Cpollute and contaminate the environment
OL,6,FThe prosecution said 66 year old Paul
OL,7,FDoherty, from Culmore Road in Derry,
OL,8,Fhad allowed waste to be illegally
OL,9,Fdisposed of on land he owned for
OL,10,Ffinancial gain.
OL,12,FDoherty was director of a company
OL,13,Fcalled Campsie Sand and Gravel which
OL,14,Fis now defunct.
OL,16,FGerry Farmer is linked by email to the
OL,17,Fburial of waste at Mobouy.
OL,19,FThe 56 year old, from Westlake in
OL,20,FDerry, is director of City Industrial
OL,21,FWaste Limited.
