OL,3,CMobuoy dump: #100m dump continues to
OL,4,Cpollute and contaminate the environment
OL,6,FA barrister said the discovery of
OL,7,Femails sent to and from Farmer show he
OL,8,Fknew the dumping was illegal and would
OL,9,Fcause pollution.
OL,11,FThe illegal superdump was discovered
OL,12,Fin 2013 but Doherty and Farmer didn't
OL,13,Fadmit their guilt until 2022.
OL,15,FMillions of pounds have since been
OL,16,Fspent just to make Mobouy safe and the
OL,17,Ffinal clean up bill could exceed #100
OL,18,Fmillion pounds.
OL,20,FDoherty and Farmer will be sentenced
OL,21,Fnext month.
